these yard sales and country

00:24:40.200 --> 00:24:43.230
auctions looking for--

00:24:43.230 --> 00:24:45.420
seeing a painting that
was discarded, saying,

00:24:45.420 --> 00:24:47.460
this guy's the next Picasso.

00:24:47.460 --> 00:24:49.110
That's not what they were doing.

00:24:49.110 --> 00:24:54.180
What they were looking for
