But in "You Can Be a Stock
Market Genius," which--

00:34:03.619 --> 00:34:05.160
what did we do in
the first 10 years?

00:34:05.160 --> 00:34:06.160
I wrote a book about it.

00:34:06.160 --> 00:34:08.043
It was "You Can Be a
