00:34:12.889 --> 00:34:13.389
at.

00:34:13.389 --> 00:34:15.424
Something strange or
different was going on.

00:34:15.424 --> 00:34:16.840
I showed people
nooks and crannies

00:34:16.840 --> 00:34:18.909
in the market, where they
could look for those.

00:34:18.909 --> 00:34:20.920
The issue there-- and
