people who can join the Value

00:49:44.860 --> 00:49:45.580
Investors Club?

00:49:45.580 --> 00:49:48.040
And if you would have gotten--
maybe two or three people

00:49:48.040 --> 00:49:50.140
in the class each year
would get an A-plus.

00:49:50.140 --> 00:49:52.060
And if you could write
up an investment thesis

00:49:52.060 --> 00:49:54.101
that I would have given
an A-plus to in my class,

00:49:54.101 --> 00:49:57.080
you can join the
club, and it's free.

00:49:57.080 --> 00:50:01.646
The only thing that you have
