00:50:01.646 --> 00:50:03.520
You have to share a
couple of your best ideas

00:50:03.520 --> 00:50:05.145
during the course of
the year, and that

00:50:05.145 --> 00:50:07.840
entitles you to see
everybody else's good ideas.

00:50:07.840 --> 00:50:10.660
And so it's just merit based.

00:50:10.660 --> 00:50:13.330
And still only 1
out of 20 applicants

00:50:13.330 --> 00:50:16.150
get in, so I think it's a
little harder than Harvard.

00:50:16.150 --> 00:50:16.898
I don't know.

00:50:16.898 --> 00:50:18.570
[LAUGHTER]

00:50:18.570 --> 00:50:23.440
But it's been going
now for 16 years.

00:50:23.440 --> 00:50:25.160
We do have a--

00:50:25.160 --> 00:50:27.160
I think it's a 45-
or 90-day delay

00:50:27.160 --> 00:50:29.620
that if you're not a member,
